Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:06.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:29.95,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:35.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:53.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:55.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:01:03.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:12.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:27.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:41.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:45.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:48.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:53.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:05.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:25.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:33.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy \Nwhose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat crew landed \Non the Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to search for a ship coating craftsman \Nto help them reach Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the adventure, Camie, a mermaid \Nwho was with them, was kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and about to be sold as a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, after storming the \Nauction house to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your squirming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Admiral Kizaru Takes Action! Sabaody \NArchipelago Thrown into Chaos"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! This town-- this \Nwhole archipelago-- is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy supposedly kicked \Na Celestial Dragon's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the auction house on Grove #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Kid and Law are there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Straw Hat bastard! \NWhat was he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he know that an admiral \Nfrom Navy Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will bring a warship here if \Nanyone hurts a Celestial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has our ship been coated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was completed yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We set sail for Fish-Man Island immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just sit around \Nwhile an admiral shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that dumbass's captain \Nis an even bigger dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever run into 'em in the \NNew World... I'll destroy 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Causing trouble with Navy Headquarters \Nwith the New World right in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a truly troublesome lot they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on getting ready to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Right away, Captain Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. Who's going to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the situation, I somehow doubt \Nthis is an all-out arrest plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Straw Hat Luffy they're after, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd like to see what \Nan admiral is actually like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious, Apoo-san! \NLet's just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hawkins! It's dangerous \Nhere! Let's set sail immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not destined to die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:32.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Holy Land of Marie Jois"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat again?! It's one \Nthing after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that entire family's bloodline?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reports indicate the presence \Nof the Straw Hat crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eustass Captain Kid and his crew, \Nand Trafalgar Law and his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen people with bounties \Nhave been confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of them, five are rookies \Nworth over 100 million each!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the key offender \Nappears to be Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who assaulted the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost contact with the \Nguards at the Human Shop--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,oh, I mean Employment Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they may have all been subdued...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this act of taking \Nthree Celestial Dragons hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a vile and unprecedented transgression!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they made any demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none at the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case may be, Sengoku-san, \Nwe'll need to take action
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,given that World Nobles are the victims here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to go. Rest easy; I won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:46.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1420)}"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your shop, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Doflamingo...! \NWhere are you right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shop has lost all credibility, and \Nthen there's Roswald's family too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely going to lash out at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something to fix things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Human trafficking \Nis so old-fashioned, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about smiles now! Smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disco, I'm giving the shop to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't be callin' me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're abandoning us during \Nthe worst crisis we've ever had?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you annoying bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you sit there blaming \Nme for your own misfortune
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a "New Era" draws ever closer, Disco-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy has given orders forcing \Nme-- no, us-- into active duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing this, what do you see \Non the horizon, Disco-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeard Pirates versus \Nthe Seven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please evacuate as far away as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No watching, please! These \Nare dangerous people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The slave I bought is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the mortars arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most of them! We're \Nhurrying to set them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has HQ said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Admiral Kizaru is coming, but \Nthe vanguard will consist of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of them?! They're coming here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! That's what they said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to remove your collar \Nnow. Are you ready, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, old man! Don't \Nbe crazy! It'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've seen a slave's collar explode before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bad idea! A very bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Franky is looking \Nfor the key as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should really wait until he \Nfinds it and brings it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Stop him, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Not here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. Just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what kind of power he used...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the one thing for sure is \Nthat he's no ordinary old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that somehow means it's okay \Nto leave Camie-chan in his hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What's Franky doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's too dangerous! \NIt won't come off without the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ringing! What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you! Now Camie's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this now?! \NDon't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your collar and handcuffs are already off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! I finally manage \Nto find 'em, but then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You found them? Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we no longer need them. \NHere, you carry this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... Th-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the hell's going on \Nhere?! Who are you, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That geezer did something mysterious again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is that old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the collar off barehanded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, almost-slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the buyers took off! You \Nshould scram while you can, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that geezer took out these \Nguards all at once too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then he must know how to use \Nmagic or some type of sorcery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got powers or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said something about \Nyour straw hat, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That straw hat suits dauntless men very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know him, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know him! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he used what's called "Haki."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about it either, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, fellows. I didn't \Nrealize other pirates were watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be quite strong to have \Nwithstood that with no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to meet \Nsuch a big-shot here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dark King" Silvers Rayleigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it. What's a legendary \Nman doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On these islands I'm Ray-san, \Nthe coating craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go calling me that other name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an old soldier now. I just \Nwant to live in peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you'll survive, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I told you all those times \Nnot to walk around these islands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving my friend, fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's this about wanting \Nto meet me, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's save that for later. \NWe first need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have the place completely \Nsurrounded, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you criminals! Release \Nthe Roswald family at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An admiral will be arriving shortly! \NI recommend immediate surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame us for whatever \Nhappens, you rookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not only caught up in this, we're \Nbeing treated as accomplices now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a good glimpse of the insanity \Nthat makes Straw Hat Luffy so notorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:17:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no complaints, but I'd rather not \Nrun into an admiral now if I can avoid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'd prefer not to use that power of \Nmine anymore, so I leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be hard for me to stay settled \Ndown if the navy discovers who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of helping \Nout a senior citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The longer we stay here, the \Nmore troops there'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, I'll help you guys out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean things up outside, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can go back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you even listening?! \NI told you two to stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what to do again and I'll start \Nby getting rid of you, Eustass-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them are captains! \NThey're spearheading the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, worth 300 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eustass Captain Kid, worth 315 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law, worth 200 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here and \Nbicker all you want. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can handle this all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them have bounties \Nwell over 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, they're so simpleminded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's gonna an all-out brawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use that chance to escape! We \Ncan't just sit around here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks... I'm sorry for \Ncausing you trouble...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me! I'm just \Nglad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie! It's my fault this happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have let you \Ngo to the amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll always cherish the memory \Nof going to the amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to apologize, Pappagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat said the same thing, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't one thing you \Nguys should be sorry for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you are my friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will rescue Camie, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow them. We're going \Nto break through in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet up on Grove #13, should \Nwe find ourselves separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grove #13? Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't "got it" at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Mr. Giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all on the verge of becoming slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to flee somewhere \Nwith these people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Be careful not to \Ndraw attention to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Straw Hat's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will repay this favor if we \Never meet again! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking credit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mortars! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! All three of 'em have powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave enough people to rescue the \Nhostages, and gather all our men here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mortars, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready! Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't either of you do anything! \NYou'll just get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you! Tell me what to do and--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Finger Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can stretch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of weird power is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! You really are \Nscrewed up in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start with Straw Hat Luffy! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, you! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Stay sharp! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't falter! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:22:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toward himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be! Are these \Nguys really rookies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Admiral Kizaru arrived yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir! But I think he'll be here shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements from the navy \Npost have arrived, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! What's going on?! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh. There's a lot more than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure got weird powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.27,0:22:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say yours is the weirdest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Swords are flying toward him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Marines are flying through \Nthe air, whirling, twirling...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are guns and even cannons \Nflying! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe my eyes! \NAnd I don't even have eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Kid-san and Law-san had powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting interesting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break Through the Siege! The \NNavy vs. the Three Captains"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
